title: EYL #204 Deion Sanders on HBCUs, NIL Rule, College Football, & The NFL
itunes:title: EYL #204 Deion Sanders on HBCUs, NIL Rule, College Football, & The NFL
description:
In episode 204, we spoke with the legendary Deion Sanders about college football, the issues facing HBCUs, his coaching career, the Jackson Mississippi water crisis, and more. 

He also talked about coaching his sons, being a leader, and his take on the Hall of Fame. #deionsanders #hbcu #Football
